  "title": "Collecting in Botswana",
  "abstract": "A mission in 1985 along a route from Gaberone to Francistown collected 77 samples, consisting of Arachis hypogaea (8), Vigna [Voandzeia] subterranea (13), Sorghum bicolor (29), Pennisetum americanum (17), Eleusine coracana (6), Vigna unguiculata (2), Sesamum sp. (1) and Macrotyloma uniflorum (1). Brief details of the samples are given.",
